OL,7,FTory MPs and housing experts are
OL,8,Fwarning Michael Gove that his
OL,9,FRenters' Reform Bill has a loophole
OL,10,Fwhich landlords could exploit to
OL,11,Fevict their tenants.
OL,13,FThe bill proposes the most
OL,14,Fsignificant reform of private renting
OL,15,Fin England and Wales since the 1988
OL,16,FHousing Act deregulated the sector in
OL,17,Ffavour of landlords. It has faced a
OL,18,Fseries of delays since it was first
OL,19,Fannounced in 2019 but is anticipated
OL,20,Fto appear in Parliament for the first
OL,21,Ftime this week.
